# OWASP ZAP Rules Configuration for Crud Application
# This file configures which security rules to apply during scanning

# Ignore false positives and expected security choices
# Format: RULE_ID	IGNORE	URL_PATTERN	PARAMETER	DESCRIPTION

# Development and testing endpoints that are expected to be accessible
10021	IGNORE	http://localhost:5172/health.*	.*	Health check endpoint (expected to be public)
10021	IGNORE	http://localhost:5172/swagger.*	.*	Swagger documentation (development only)

# Allow Cross-Origin Resource Sharing (CORS) for development
10020	IGNORE	.*	.*	CORS enabled for Angular development

# Ignore SSL/TLS warnings for local development
10003	IGNORE	http://localhost.*	.*	Local development over HTTP (not HTTPS)

# Content Security Policy (CSP) - May be implemented later
10038	IGNORE	.*	.*	CSP header not implemented yet (future enhancement)

# X-Frame-Options - May be implemented later  
10020	IGNORE	.*	.*	X-Frame-Options header not implemented yet (future enhancement)

# Authentication bypass - Expected for public endpoints
10106	IGNORE	http://localhost:5172/api/people.*	.*	Public API endpoints (no auth required initially)
10106	IGNORE	http://localhost:5172/api/auth/register.*	.*	Registration endpoint (must be public)

# SQL Injection - Protected by Entity Framework
40018	IGNORE	.*	.*	Using Entity Framework ORM (parameterized queries)

# Directory browsing - Expected for SPA routes
10033	IGNORE	.*	.*	Angular SPA routing (expected directory structure)

# Information disclosure - Development endpoints
10094	IGNORE	http://localhost:5172/swagger.*	.*	Development documentation endpoint
10094	IGNORE	http://localhost:5172/health.*	.*	Health check endpoint for monitoring

# Cross-Site Request Forgery (CSRF) - Planned for future implementation
10202	IGNORE	.*	.*	CSRF protection planned for future authentication implementation